Class ClassLoaderList

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.vm.ClassLoaderList
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Restorable<ClassLoaderList>, Cloneable, Iterable<ClassLoaderInfo>

    public class ClassLoaderList
extends Object
implements Cloneable, Iterable<ClassLoaderInfo>, Restorable<ClassLoaderList>
    container for all ClassLoaderInfos that are in the current state. It is important to keep this as canonically (search globally) sorted list so that we can use the iterator for state matching
